{"type":null,"faqId":49487,"title":"开启蓝牙并与其他设备配对","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.20833333in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:13pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"开启蓝牙\"XE \"关闭蓝牙\"XE \"蓝牙配对\"XE \"取消蓝牙配对\"XE \"取消配对\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 1  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189794\" style=\"width:0.24583334in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 2  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“蓝牙”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 3  </span><span>点击“蓝牙”开关，开启蓝牙。手机将自动搜索并列出可用的蓝牙设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤 4  </span><span>点击要配对的设备，根据屏幕提示进行配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>后续处理</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若要取消配对，点击已配对设备名称旁边的“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=189795\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，然后点击“取消配对”。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n